  "reference_number": "RUS1673",
  "remarks": "\nAndrey Vladimirovich CHIBIS is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because: 1) he is Governor of Murmansk, and therefore, a regional governor of the Russian Federation and an involved person in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine; and 2) he is or has engaged in the partial mobilisation of military reservists in Murmansk region, a policy and action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
